libs.java.extension.collections.observable

Class NotificationList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • libs.java.extension.collections.observable.NotificationCollection<E>
      • libs.java.extension.collections.observable.NotificationList<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.util.List<E>

    public class NotificationList<E>
extends NotificationCollection<E>
implements java.util.List<E>
    A decorated List which allows notification on different list operation. Simple usage is
    List a = new NotificationList<>(new ArrayList<>(), null, new NotificationListener() {
    Author:
    Kuldeep
